---
import BaseLayout from "../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import SiteHeader from "../../components/SiteHeader.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
	title="For Bounty Hunters — ChristmasTreeTurner.com"
	description="AI came up empty. This is a boots-on-the-ground detective case with real bounties for real leads."
>
	<SiteHeader />

	<main id="main-content" class="mt-24">
		<div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto">
			<a href="/" class="font-mono text-sm tracking-widest uppercase text-muted hover:text-text transition-colors mb-8 inline-block">&larr; Back to Home</a>

			<h1 class="uppercase tracking-tight text-4xl md:text-6xl italic mb-4 text-red" style="font-family: 'Tay Highbeams', sans-serif;">For Bounty Hunters</h1>

			<h2 class="uppercase tracking-tight text-2xl italic mt-12 mb-4" style="font-family: 'Tay Highbeams', sans-serif;">The Challenge</h2>

			<p class="text-lg mb-4 leading-relaxed">We've hit a wall. AI tools scraped the internet dry and came up empty. This isn't a keyboard mystery anymore&mdash;it's a boots-on-the-ground detective case.</p>

			<p class="text-lg mb-4 leading-relaxed">A Texas family is hunting the origins of their full-size mechanical Christmas Tree Turner (SpinCraft, Milwaukee, Patent 2733032). It exists. It works. But the company, the manufacturer, the distribution chain&mdash;all ghosts.</p>

			<p class="text-lg mb-4 leading-relaxed">If you're the type who digs through archives, haunts estate sales, or knows how to work a microfiche machine, we need you.</p>

			<h2 class="uppercase tracking-tight text-2xl italic mt-12 mb-4" style="font-family: 'Tay Highbeams', sans-serif;">Active Bounties</h2>

			<ul class="pl-5 list-disc grid gap-2 mb-6 text-lg">
				<li><span class="font-bold">$250</span> — Print advertisement (magazine, newspaper, or catalog with publication date)</li>
				<li><span class="font-bold">$250</span> — Patent documentation (filing notes, diagrams, correspondence tied to Patent 2733032)</li>
				<li><span class="font-bold">$250</span> — Working unit (any surviving example with photo/video evidence)</li>
				<li><span class="font-bold">$500</span> — Verified family connection (documents tying Ulrich family to manufacturing/distribution)</li>
				<li><span class="font-bold">$500</span> — Verified family photo (unseen photo of Ulrich family member with unit in commercial context)</li>
				<li><span class="font-bold">$50</span> — Find a sponsor (refer someone who commits to a sponsorship tier)</li>
			</ul>

			<h2 class="uppercase tracking-tight text-2xl italic mt-12 mb-4" style="font-family: 'Tay Highbeams', sans-serif;">The Rules</h2>

			<p class="text-lg mb-4 leading-relaxed">Bounties are paid as donations to a teacher or school of your choice. Not cash to you. Evidence must be verified before payout.</p>

			<h2 class="uppercase tracking-tight text-2xl italic mt-12 mb-4" style="font-family: 'Tay Highbeams', sans-serif;">How to Claim</h2>

			<p class="text-lg mb-4 leading-relaxed">Email <a href="mailto:clark@superfun.team" class="text-accent hover:underline">clark@superfun.team</a> with your evidence, or use the contact form on this site. First verified claim wins. Multiple claims eligible if you find multiple leads. Good hunting.</p>

			<div class="bg-accent text-white p-8 mt-12">
				<h2 class="uppercase tracking-tight text-2xl italic mb-3" style="font-family: 'Tay Highbeams', sans-serif;">Ready to Help?</h2>
				<p class="text-white/80 text-sm mb-4 leading-relaxed">Send us what you find — or just say hello.</p>
				<a href="/#contact" class="inline-block py-3 px-6 bg-white text-accent font-mono text-xs uppercase tracking-widest hover:bg-white/90 transition-colors">Submit a Lead</a>
			</div>
		</div>

		<footer class="border-t border-border pt-16 mt-16 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
			<p class="font-mono text-sm tracking-widest uppercase text-muted">
				This is a personal historical research project. No commercial use intended.
			</p>
			<p class="font-mono text-sm tracking-widest uppercase text-muted mt-2">
				Help, questions, and press inquiries: clark@superfun.team
			</p>
		</footer>
	</main>
</BaseLayout>
